Package: rilate
Title: Randomization Inference for the Local Average Treatment Effect
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Haoge", "Chang", , "hgchang1508@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Arya", "Gadage", role = "aut"))
Description: Implements randomization-based inferential procedures for the Local
    Average Treatment Effect (LATE) in randomized experiments with
    noncompliance. Provides Anderson-Rubin permutation tests, p-values, and
    confidence sets that are finite-sample valid for the sharp null and
    asymptotically valid for the LATE under treatment-effect heterogeneity, and
    remain robust when compliance rates are low. Supports covariate adjustment
    via linear regression to improve precision.
